rows.label: bf06440100_0030
rows.name: Shin told me to look at the world ahead.

rows.label: bf06440100_0040
rows.name: I thought he was talking about the future...

rows.label: bf06440100_0045
rows.name: But maybe he meant human history?

rows.label: bf06440100_0050
rows.name: And that is the key to why they fight...?

rows.label: bf06440100_0070
rows.name: If... If that is the case...

rows.label: bf06440100_0080
rows.name:
Perhaps I...never should have been
sealed away after all...
